Flappy ZigZag is a simple extension for the Chrome browser that provides a fun and challenging gaming experience for users. In this game, the player controls a flying bird and must navigate through obstacles by moving in a zigzag pattern. The player's task is to keep the bird flying for as long as possible and score as high as possible. Flappy ZigZag is a simple yet highly addictive game suitable for all ages and can be played anytime, anywhere on the Chrome browser.

HOW TO PLAY 
Tap or click on screen to play
